The Channels &amp; Digitalization function enables end-to-end seamless connectivity for UOB customers across all physical and digital touchpoints of the Bank. Designed to be in tune with our customers’ banking preferences, we strive to enhance engagement and deliver exemplary experiences across our network of branches, self-service machines and digital platforms.

Responsibilities
• &nbsp;Development of web content for marketing and thought leadership purposes. This includes research, ideation, writing, copy editing, selection of images, designing infographics.
• &nbsp;Conducting market research on the FinTech industry.

Requirements
• &nbsp;You are curious, willing to learn and a problem-solver.
• &nbsp;You spotted the typo in the sentence above.
• &nbsp;You think strategically and communicate effectively.
• &nbsp;You are a flexible writer, and are equally comfortable penning short, punchy &nbsp;copy or longer, thought-provoking pieces.
• &nbsp;You have a keen eye for details, and a flair for web/graphic design.
• &nbsp;You believe in producing work that can make an impact on people's lives and business success, while understanding the need to adhere to corporate/brand guidelines.
• Video editing skills are a bonus.
• Please be prepared to share samples of your creative work.